;; A minimal robot as a capability-component graph: sensor → planner → actuator.
;; The components are listed OUT of dataflow order on purpose — the topics are
;; named capabilities (:topic/scan, :topic/cmd), so the broker derives the boot
;; order from the capability graph (a topic's publisher boots before its
;; subscriber), not from this list. Boot with the default policy:
;;   aiueos up examples/robot/robot.aiueos.edn
{:aiueos/system :robot
 :aiueos/components ["actuator.edn" "planner.edn" "sensor.edn"]}
